Step 1: Start
Step 2: Initialize empty assignment list
Step 3: Set assignment ID counter = 1

Step 4: Repeat
    Step 4.1: Display menu
        1. Add Assignment
        2. View Assignments
        3. Submit Assignment
        4. Delete Assignment
        5. Exit

    Step 4.2: Read user choice

    Step 4.3: If choice == 1
                Call Add Assignment
              Else if choice == 2
                Call View Assignments
              Else if choice == 3
                Call Submit Assignment
              Else if choice == 4
                Call Delete Assignment
              Else if choice == 5
                Exit loop
              Else
                Print "Invalid Choice"

Step 5: Stop
